OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1780398175
OL,3,CFather raising money for brain tumour
OL,4,Cresearch after wife, 33, dies
OL,6,FA father whose wife died from a brain
OL,7,Ftumour just six months after being
OL,8,Fdiagnosed is entering a triathlon, all
OL,9,Fwhile still learning to swim.
OL,11,FAlan Johnstone from Dumfries is aiming
OL,12,Fto compete in the Austria Ironman
OL,13,Fcompetition in June 2027. He'll face a
OL,14,F2.4-mile open-water swim and a 112-
OL,15,Fmile bike ride before running a
OL,16,Fmarathon.
OL,18,FAlan says it will be his hardest
OL,19,Fchallenge yet, because he is still
OL,20,Flearning to swim.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
