PN,35102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1780398175
OL,3,CFather raising money for brain tumour
OL,4,Cresearch after wife, 33, dies
OL,6,FIt's to raise money for the Brain
OL,7,FTumour charity, after his wife and
OL,8,Fchildhood sweetheart, Anneka, died at
OL,9,Fthe age of 33 in 2019.
OL,11,FTheir daughter, Sienna, was 13 months
OL,12,Fold when Anneka died from an
OL,13,Faggressive glioblastoma.
OL,15,FAlan said: "Sienna had just been born
OL,16,Fand we had this six month period that
OL,17,Fwas just lovely, peaceful. It was
OL,18,Fgreat to be in a loving family.
OL,20,F"Then Anneka became dizzy and we
OL,21,Fdidn't think it was anything serious.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1780398175
OL,3,CFather raising money for brain tumour
OL,4,Cresearch after wife, 33, dies
OL,6,F"I took her to A&E and we got her in
OL,7,Ffor some scans, and they told us they
OL,8,Ffound something on the scan, even then
OL,9,FI was scared, but I probably didn't
OL,10,Frealise what it would be.
OL,12,F"Two or three days later we were told
OL,13,Fit was a brain tumour.
OL,15,F"Your heart is ripped out. All of our
OL,16,Flives got ripped apart."
OL,18,FAnneka died in November 2019, just six
OL,19,Fmonths after her diagnosis.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1780398175
OL,3,CFather raising money for brain tumour
OL,4,Cresearch after wife, 33, dies
OL,6,FHe continued: "There are no words to
OL,7,Fdescribe how tough it was for all of
OL,8,Fus.
OL,10,F"Anneka was always smiling, always
OL,11,Ffull of energy. She would've been the
OL,12,Fbest mum to Sienna, but unfortunately
OL,13,Fshe didn't get the chance."
OL,15,FBrain tumours are the biggest cancer
OL,16,Fkiller of children and young adults
OL,17,Funder the age of 40 in Scotland.
OL,19,FIn the past few years, Alan has raised
OL,20,Fmore than #100,000 for the brain
OL,21,Ftumour charity.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
