PN,35105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1780398175
OL,3,CFather raising money for brain tumour
OL,4,Cresearch after wife, 33, dies
OL,6,FHe's now preparing for his next
OL,7,Ffundraising challenge in June 2027:
OL,8,Fthe Austrian Ironman competition.
OL,10,FAlan says it will be his hardest
OL,11,Fchallenge yet, because he is still
OL,12,Flearning to swim.
OL,14,FAlan said: "Previously if I was doing
OL,15,Fa front crawl, I'd do a length but I
OL,16,Fwouldn't breath at all. So I'd get to
OL,17,Fthe other end of the pool and be
OL,18,Fknackered.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1780398175
OL,3,CFather raising money for brain tumour
OL,4,Cresearch after wife, 33, dies
OL,6,F"I'm not so concerned about the
OL,7,Frunning and cycling, but the swimming
OL,8,Fis the thing that scares me the most."
OL,10,FAlan's Ironman challenge has already
OL,11,Fraised more than #23,000.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
